verses.text: \w It|strong="H3117"\w* \w is|strong="H3117"\w* good \w to|strong="H3117"\w* give thanks \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H3117"\w* \nd Lord\nd*, \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w sing|strong="H7892"\w* praise \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w your|strong="H3117"\w* name, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* Most High,

\w to|strong="H3068"\w* declare \w your|strong="H3068"\w* love \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* morning, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* faithfulness \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* night,

\w For|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* make \w me|strong="H5921"\w* glad \w by|strong="H5921"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* deeds, \nd Lord\nd*, \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* work \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* hands \w I|strong="H5921"\w* will ring \w out|strong="H5921"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* \w joy|strong="H5921"\w*.

\w How|strong="H3588"\w* great \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w works|strong="H4639"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*; \w how|strong="H3588"\w* deep \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* thoughts!
\w The|strong="H3068"\w* insensitive cannot know, nor \w can|strong="H4100"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fool understand,

\w that|strong="H3045"\w*, though \w the|strong="H3045"\w* wicked flourish \w like|strong="H3808"\w* grass, \w and|strong="H3045"\w* evildoers \w all|strong="H3045"\w* blossom, \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* perish forever.

\w For|strong="H3068"\w* see! \w Your|strong="H3068"\w* enemies, \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w For|strong="H3068"\w* see! \w Your|strong="H3068"\w* enemies perish, \w all|strong="H5769"\w* evildoers \w are|strong="H3068"\w* scattered.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w lift|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* honor, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* anoint \w me|strong="H3588"\w* afresh \w with|strong="H3068"\w* oil.

\w My|strong="H7311"\w* eyes will feast \w on|strong="H7161"\w* \w my|strong="H7311"\w* foes, \w and|strong="H8081"\w* \w my|strong="H7311"\w* ears will hear \w of|strong="H7161"\w* \w the|strong="H7311"\w* doom \w of|strong="H7161"\w* \w the|strong="H7311"\w* wicked.

\w The|strong="H5921"\w* righteous \w will|strong="H5869"\w* sprout \w like|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* palm, \w will|strong="H5869"\w* grow \w like|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cedar \w of|strong="H5869"\w* Lebanon.

\w In|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* house \w of|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H6662"\+w*\nd* \w are|strong="H6662"\w* they planted, \w in|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* courts \w of|strong="H6662"\w* our God they \w will|strong="H6662"\w* \w sprout|strong="H6524"\w*.
